<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٩٢٢ - حدثنا عمر عن ابن <span class="c2">(جريج)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> عن عطاء قال: يحنث قال اللَّه <span class="c2">(تعالى)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>: ﴿تَأْكُلُونَ لَحْمًا <span class="c2">(طَرِيًّا)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>﴾.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
